OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJohn Lewis staff wearing   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbodycams amid theft rise   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Retail staff are being trained to      
OL,6, tackle violence from shoplifters after 
OL,7, an increase in reports of the crime.   
OL,9,FThe Welsh Retail Consortium (WRC) said 
OL,10,Fthere was a more than a 30% rise in    
OL,11,Fviolence and abuse towards staff in    
OL,12,FCardiff between 2021 and 2022.         
OL,14,FJohn Lewis is one company offering     
OL,15,F"de-escalation" training, with the WRC 
OL,16,Fsaying stores need more support from   
OL,17,Fpolice.                                
OL,19,FThe Home Office said it had invested a 
OL,20,Frecord amount into policing.           
